        public RectangleA​(int w,

        A constructor that receives two integers as parameters, the first is the width of the rectangle and the second Is the height. The southwest point will be at the beginning of the axes (0, 0). The length and breadth must be really positive integers. If any of them are not, the attribute will be initialized to be 1
        Parameters:
